Original 3D cloud-architecture tower-defense sim by Kostyantyn Pshenychnyy.
Play as a cloud architect: place CDN, database, firewall, and related services
to survive rising traffic and DDoS pressure.

Vendored runtime libraries:
- three.js r128 (local vendor/three.min.js)
- Tailwind CSS utilities prebuilt (local vendor/tailwind.min.css; zero runtime CDN)

FreeToolOnline adaptations (2026-07-21, game-discovery-loop fire180):
- robots noindex on iframe document
- dropped assets/gameplay.gif preview
- localStorage namespaced to ftol:serversurvivaltd:*
- title "Server Survival TD"
